headline: Republic Services Named One of the World's Most Ethical Companies for Seventh Time
summary: For the seventh year, Republic Services, Inc. (NYSE: RSG) has received the World's Most Ethical Companies® recognition by Ethisphere, a global leader in defining and advancing the standards of the ethical business practices. Republic Services is one of 136 companies spanning 19 countries and 44 industries to be recognized in 2025.
